Carolyn M. Tastad

Age : 55Public asset : 6,248,672 USDLinked companies :  Procter & Gamble Co -  Kellogg Company 





Summary 



Ms. Carolyn M. Tastad is Group President-North American Selling Operations at Procter & Gamble Co.She is on the Board of Directors at Kellogg Co., Grocery Manufacturers Association and Cincinnati Museum Center. Ms. Tastad was previously employed as Member-Management Board by Wella GmbH.



