Wella GmbH


                  Wella GmbH manufactures hair care and cosmetic products. It offers cuts, color, perms and other hair services along with facial waxing and hair care products. It makes and distributes hair care products for sale in professional hair salons. The company was founded in 1880 and is headquartered in Darmstadt, Germany.                





